data.description: Agents: Offers are due on Sunday April 28th at  Noon.  Welcome home to 230 Ironwood Manor Drive, a townhome nestled in the heart of Silver Spring, MD. This meticulously maintained residence boasts three spacious stories, offering an abundance of living space. Step inside to the welcoming living room, adorned with gleaming hardwood floors that extend throughout the home. The high tray ceiling and intricate crown molding create a sense of grandeur. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring sleek stone countertops, a breakfast bar for casual dining, and a double oven for culinary adventures. The backsplash adds a touch of style and complements the stainless-steel refrigerator. The primary bathroom is a sanctuary of relaxation, complete with a double sink vanity and a luxurious tile shower. The additional bathroom features a convenient shower. Outside, enjoy the privacy and tranquility of your deck, perfect for al fresco dining or simply soaking up the sun. The pergola casts an elegant shadow, creating a cozy ambiance for outdoor gatherings. This townhome is ready to move in and offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Silver Spring.
